Așteaptă sus !

986
01:24:58.537 --> 01:24:59.620
Am înțeles.

987
01:25:15.287 --> 01:25:18.120
- Ce surpriză !
- Da.


988
01:25:18.287 --> 01:25:19.620
De necrezut !

989
01:25:19.787 --> 01:25:21.120
De ce ești aici ?

990
01:25:22.162 --> 01:25:23.245
Pentru reuniune.

991
01:25:24.037 --> 01:25:25.745
Reuniunea de liceu ?

992
01:25:26.620 --> 01:25:29.245
